extracted_information: Detailed information regarding home decor dropshipping products, suppliers, profit margins, and trending items for 2025.

features.name: Luxury Feather Floor Lamp
features.description: Floor lamp designed as a luxury home decor item. High-ticket item. Seller: Venetto Design (website, FB Ad). Source: AliExpress.

seller_website_features: Spin to win popup for perks

features.name: Tiger Eyes Street Art
features.description: Signature picture or artwork for room theme. Seller: Kanvas Kingdom (website, FB Ad). Source: AliExpress.

supplier_features: 2% off on orders above five pieces

features.name: Luminous Luxury Chandelier
features.description: Extravagant high-end interior lighting for dining rooms. Seller: Noosh Decor (website, FB Ad). Source: AliExpress.

features.name: Outdoor String Lights
features.description: Lighting accessories for any event, available in multiple designs and sizes. Best for cross-selling with gardening products.

technical_details.durability: Bulbs should be weatherproof and not easily shatter.

features.name: Wall Letter Signs
features.description: In-demand wall decor product made of plastic, vinyl, or wood. Straightforward to install using adhesives.

features.name: Mini Wood Decorative Books
features.description: Home decor item resembling a collection of books. Available in different designs, sizes, colors, and frames. Made of high-quality, termite-resistant wood.

features.name: Throw Pillows
features.description: Adds comfort and cuteness to homes, enhancing bedrooms, sofas, and living rooms. Made of down-feather, fiber, or foam. Covers can be cotton, burlap, velvet, satin, etc. Highly in demand.

technical_details.profit_strategy: Sell made of high-quality materials (faux fur, leather, velvet, silk) for higher profit margins.

features.name: Thermal Insulated Curtains
features.description: Designed as an insulation layer to regulate room temperature. Made of heat-resistant and cold-resistant materials. Some have double/triple acrylic foam layers. Varies in fabric type, energy efficiency, and price.

features.name: Picture Frame Set
features.description: Excellent for displaying memories or pictures. Endless selection of designs (modern, contemporary). Made of wood, metal, plastic, or glass.

features.name: Rug Pads Grippers
features.description: Used to attach rugs and carpets to the floor. Made of durable slip-resistant latex rubber. Versatile for different floor types (tiles, hardwood). Easily removable, washable, long shelf life.

features.name: Non-Slip Bath Mat
features.description: Protects from slippery bathroom floors while adding visual appeal. Available in various shapes (oval, circular, square, rectangular). Made of rubber, bamboo, or polyester.

features.name: Reversible Sofa Slipcover
features.description: Protective covers for sofas, reversible. Some are water repellent, others resistant to stains, dirt, scratches. Available in various designs specific to sofa types (three-seater, two-seater). Can have a luxury feel.

features.name: Scented Candles
features.description: Creates ambiance of well-being and relaxation. Made by mixing fragrant oil with wax, emits pleasant aromas (apple, vanilla, chocolate, jasmine, sandalwood). Does not emit smoke. High market demand, low cost product.

technical_details.niche_idea: Focus on aromatherapy store (sell with essential oils, incense, bath bombs).

features.name: LED Moon Lamp
features.description: LED Lamp resembling a glowing moon. Portable, long battery life. Different light modes, adjustable brightness, stylish wooden stand. Viral on TikTok.

technical_details.variation: Automated LED Moon Lamp with remote control.

features.name: Rustic Wall Sconces
features.description: Unique lighting option to add light layers. Wide selection made of metal, plastic, glass, and wood. Available in retro, modern, or classic designs.

features.name: Vintage Bathroom Canvas
features.description: Artwork for bathroom walls, painting or printed images. Similar to picture frames, mostly wood, also metal, vinyl, or plastic. High demand.

features.name: Digital LED Clock
features.description: Modern watch showing time digitally. Attaches to wall, desk, or table. Made of durable plastic, rechargeable battery. Some include USB ports, mini speakers, adjustable brightness settings.

features.name: Ceramic Flower Vase
features.description: Latest home-decor item. Comes in different colors, styles, and shapes (contemporary, modern, minimalistic). Durable, high-quality, long-lasting. Perfect for decorating tables, shelves, mantels, dining rooms, bathrooms, patios.

features.name: Artificial Hanging Eucalyptus Plant
features.description: Provides features of authentic eucalyptus plants without maintenance. Made of high-quality plastic and fabric (polyester), long-lasting, easy to clean.

technical_details.marketing_strategy: Product bundling (offer pack of 4-5 artificial plants for discount).

features.name: Over The Door Hooks
features.description: Set of hooks to manage garments, kitchen utensils, accessories. Made of metals (aluminum, iron) for durability. Affordable plastic or wood options available. Different sizes and color options.

features.name: Food Storage Containers
features.description: Home improvement product for the kitchen. Airtight, keeps moisture out. Water and cold resistant for refrigeration. Multiple colors and shapes.

features.name: Woven Laundry Hamper
features.description: Functional home decor product in high demand. Made of jute and cotton threads (eco-friendly, durable). Machine woven or hand woven. Soft, foldable for storage.

technical_details.sourcing_tip: Source unique designs from Etsy to differentiate.

features.name: Bedside Lamp
features.description: Graceful design creating pleasant ambiance. Available in different designs and shapes (spherical, mushroom-shaped, cylindrical). Made of metal, glass, wood, and ceramic.

features.name: AutoDS
features.description: AutoDS Marketplace offers private home decor dropshipping suppliers and also functions as a supplier itself with a warehouse. Linked to automated order fulfillment system 'Fulfilled by AutoDS'.

features: Option to send branded 'Thank You' card

features.description: Ideal for American consumers, with many distribution centers and a vast variety of home niche items.

features: Tax exemption program (for state, country, or federal tax ID holders)
Free 2-day delivery for over 1 million products

features.name: Walmart
features.description: Great for American shoppers, offering diverse home decor products and fast delivery.

features: Price match policy (refund for price difference if product goes on sale within return period)
Free & fast shipping (next-day delivery for US consumers)

features.name: AliExpress
features.description: Online retail marketplace connecting with Chinese home decor manufacturers and suppliers.

features: Massive variety of home decor products
Buyer & seller protection (guarantees quality and delivery)

features.name: CJDropshipping
features.description: Online dropshipping platform built by experienced dropshippers.

features: Warehouses in 30+ countries (US, Europe, Canada for faster shipping)
Private labeling services (customize products under own brand)

features.name: Amazon
features.description: World's largest eCommerce company and reliable dropshipping supplier for home decor products.

features.name: Wayfair
features.description: Niche dropshipping supplier specializing in home improvement products.

features: Vast product catalog (15 million+ products from 11,000+ global suppliers)
MYWAY program (exclusive items, free & same-day shipping for members)
Flexible payment options (credit cards, Apple Pay, PayPal, Wire Transfer)

features.name: Costway
features.description: Niche dropshipping supplier focusing on home-decor products, a top retailer in the US.

features: Dropshipping program (affordable pricing, 2-day shipping, 3-month product warranty)
Built-in blogging feature (SEO for organic traffic)
Wix App Market (dropshipping apps and tools)
Zero upfront investment (no capital needed to start selling)
Low selling fees (5% or $0.40, whichever is higher, paid after sale)
